Title: Conspiracy Theory
Plot: The team investigates a suicide case, believing that the main reason of her death is a nervous breakdown, but Ducky believes that she was actually murdered. FBI Special Agent Fornell helps them in the investigation. The team discovers that the dead woman was involved in a love triangle and that this may have contributed to her death.
GuestStars: Brigid Brannagh, Dan Ziskie, Jennifer Dundas, Brian Dietzen, Hilary Angelo, Molly Hagan, Dean McDermott, Kevin Quigley, Jonathan Redford, Joe Spano
